      "name": "Dermal Barrier",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "modules/cyberpunk-5e/assets/cyberware_icons/dermal_barrier.png",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "The juggernaut can deploy its barrier as a bonus action, reducing its speed by 10 feet. At the end of each of its turns, the juggernaut decides which way a 150- foot cone faces and whether the cone is active. The juggernaut has three-quarters cover against attacks and effects from creatures and vehicles in the cone. Creatures of the juggneraut's choice within 5 feet of it also benefit from this cover. Overdrive Engine (Recharges on a Short or Long Rest.) The juggernaut can take 3d8 fire damage and take an additional action on its turn.",
